OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA dry day with plenty of
OL,6,Fsunny spells. Fresh easterly winds,
OL,7,Fthese strong over hills where it will
OL,8,Ffeel much cooler.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FEarly
OL,11,Fcloud and mist clearing Thursday and
OL,12,FFriday to give long sunny spells.
OL,13,FBreezy Thursday, easing Friday.
OL,14,FCloudier Saturday, but with sunny
OL,15,Fintervals and a risk of showers.
OL,16,FTemperatures increasing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
